    <string name="jail_report_work_profile_none">No secondary profile is detected on this device, so main-profile data would still be visible to this app.</string>
    <string name="jail_report_work_profile_present">This app is also installed in another profile. If that profile is managed/work, that copy is isolated from main-profile app data.</string>
    <string name="jail_report_work_profile_missing">Another profile appears to exist on this device, but this app is only in the main profile. Installing it in that profile may reduce data exposure from the main profile.</string>
    <string name="jail_report_work_profile_shared_channels">Even across profiles, some channels remain shared: notifications, clipboard, shared media, and screen content while the app is visible.</string>
    <string name="jail_report_network_internet">This app has network access. The Jail tunnel can change the network path, but the app still sees its own requests, DNS lookups, and response timing.</string>
